    class CarDetailView(generic.DetailView):
        model = CarInstance
        template_name = &#39;car_detail&#39;
        slug_field = &#39;title&#39;
        slug_url_kwarg = &#39;car_model&#39;

More information can be found in [**`get_object()`**](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/2.2/ref/class-based-views/mixins-single-object/#django.views.generic.detail.SingleObjectMixin.get_object) documentation.

